pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh-cn/post/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E9%A9%AC%E7%8E%8B%E5%A0%86%E5%B8%9B%E4%B9%A6%E7%89%88/</guid><description>01 道可道也，非恒道也。名可名也，非恒名也。无名万物之始也，有名万物之母也。故：恒无欲也，以观其眇；恒有欲也，以观其徼。两者同出，异名同谓。玄</description></item><item><title>道德经英文:一到三章</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh-cn/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%91/%E4%B8%80%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%A0/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh-cn/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%91/%E4%B8%80%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%A0/</guid><description>第一章 道可道，非常道；名可名，非常名。 The Way that can be told of is not an Unvarying Way; The names that can be named are not unvarying names. 威利用the way来翻译道，西方人看重方法。 无名，天地之始</description></item><item><title>道德经英文:四到六章</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh-cn/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%91/%E5%9B%9B%E5%88%B0%E5%85%AD%E7%AB%A0/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh-cn/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%91/%E5%9B%9B%E5%88%B0%E5%85%AD%E7%AB%A0/</guid><description>ref https://jesselau.com/daodejingen2/ https://jesselau.com/tags/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%91%E6%9C%AC/</description></item><item><title>元道经 注解</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh-cn/reading/%E5%85%83%E9%81%93%E7%BB%8F%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%A3/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh-cn/reading/%E5%85%83%E9%81%93%E7%BB%8F%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%A3/</guid><description>太上老君元道真经注解 合明子隐芝内秀注 释题曰：元者，本也，始也。道者，太上真一之道也。经者，径也，本始之真元。此经最妙，故曰真经。 元道者，老君</description></item><item><title>八十八佛大忏悔文</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh-cn/post/%E5%85%AB%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E4%BD%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%8F%E6%82%94%E6%96%87/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh-cn/post/%E5%85%AB%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E4%BD%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%8F%E